texts.label: paragraph
texts.orig: Need a handy way to list all the email accounts and their passwords?
texts.text: Need a handy way to list all the email accounts and their passwords?

texts.label: code
texts.orig: select CONCAT(mail_name,"@",name) as email_address,accounts.password from mail left join domains on domains.id=mail.dom_id left join accounts on accounts.id=mail.account_id;
texts.text: select CONCAT(mail_name,"@",name) as email_address,accounts.password from mail left join domains on domains.id=mail.dom_id left join accounts on accounts.id=mail.account_id;
